e Graph Dataset</a> - Graph of the development history and file metadata of >80 million software projects from various forges (GitHub, Gitlab, Debian, PyPI, Google Code, etc) in a deduplicated and unified representation (<a href=\"https://dl.acm.org/citation.cfm?id=3341907\">paper here</a>).</li>","updatedAt":"2020-04-27T18:26:09.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Tools</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://github.com/chaoss/grimoirelab-perceval\">Perceval</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/chaoss/grimoirelab-perceval\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">261</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCount\":261,\"repo\":\"chaoss/grimoirelab-perceval\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END--> - Fetch repository data from tens of back-ends.</li>","updatedAt":"2020-04-27T17:57:11.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Data Sets</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://rvantonder.github.io/CryptOSS/\">Cryptocurrency GitHub Activity and Market Cap Dataset</a> - Activity such as commits, stars, prices, and market cap of over 200 cryptocurrency projects on GitHub over time. Raw, historic data is also <a href=\"https://zenodo.org/record/2595588#.XRuzuBNKhSM\">available</a>.</li>","updatedAt":"2019-07-02T19:47:31.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Tools</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://github.com/rvantonder/CryptOSS\">CryptOSS</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/rvantonder/CryptOSS\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">8</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCount\":8,\"repo\":\"rvantonder/CryptOSS\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END--> - Mine GitHub activity and market cap data for cryptocurrency projects.</li>","updatedAt":"2019-07-02T19:47:31.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Data Sets</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://zenodo.org/record/2652487#.XRnvomUzb0o\">Linux Kernel 4.21 Call Graphs</a> - The Linux Kernel 4.21 Call Graphs produced using <a href=\"https://github.com/dspinellis/cscout/\">CScout</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/dspinellis/cscout/\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">162</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCount\":162,\"repo\":\"dspinellis/cscout\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END-->.</li>","updatedAt":"2019-07-01T11:37:32.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Data Sets</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://slebok.github.io/zoo/\">Grammar Zoo</a> - Collection of grammars of DSLs and GPLs, some extracted from metamodels and document schemata.</li>","updatedAt":"2019-06-30T18:59:40.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Data Sets</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://www.inf.u-szeged.hu/~ferenc/papers/UnifiedBugDataSet/\">Unified Bug Dataset</a> - Static source code based datasets which includes the Bugcatchers Bug Dataset, the <a href=\"http://bug.inf.usi.ch/index.php\">Bug Prediction Dataset</a>, the <a href=\"https://www.st.cs.uni-saarland.de/softevo/bug-data/eclipse/\">Eclipse Bug Dataset</a>, the <a href=\"http://www.inf.u-szeged.hu/~ferenc/papers/GitHubBugDataSet/\">GitHub Bug Dataset</a>, some datasets from the <a href=\"http://promise.site.uottawa.ca/SERepository/datasets-page.html\">PROMISE</a> repository.</li>","updatedAt":"2019-06-12T16:20:21.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Data Sets</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://www.inf.u-szeged.hu/~ferenc/papers/GitHubBugDataSet/\">GitHub Bug Dataset</a> - Bug Dataset of 15 Java open-source projects characterized by static source code metrics.</li>","updatedAt":"2019-05-27T13:05:27.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Tools</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://github.com/SpoonLabs/coming/\">Coming</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/SpoonLabs/coming/\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">81</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCount\":81,\"repo\":\"SpoonLabs/coming\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END--> - A Java framework for analyzing code changes and mining instances of change patterns from Git repositories.</li>","updatedAt":"2019-05-12T17:05:36.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Tools</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://github.com/tushartushar/Puppeteer\">Puppeteer</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/tushartushar/Puppeteer\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">38</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCount\":38,\"repo\":\"tushartushar/Puppeteer\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END--> - Detect configuration smells in Puppet code.</li>","updatedAt":"2019-05-09T15:03:31.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Tools</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://github.com/tushartushar/DbDeo\">DbDeo</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/tushartushar/DbDeo\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">13</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCount\":13,\"repo\":\"tushartushar/DbDeo\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END--> - Extract embedded SQL statements and detect database schema smells.</li>","updatedAt":"2019-05-09T11:59:19.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Tools</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://www.designite-tools.com\">Designite</a> - Compute source code metrics and detect a variety of implementation, design, and architecture smells for C#.</li>","updatedAt":"2019-05-09T11:56:58.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Tools</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://github.com/tushartushar/DesigniteJava\">DesigniteJava</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/tushartushar/DesigniteJava\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">138</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCount\":138,\"repo\":\"tushartushar/DesigniteJava\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END--> - Compute source code metrics and detect a variety of implementation and design smells for Java.</li>","updatedAt":"2019-05-09T11:56:58.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Research Outlets</h2>","itemHTML":"<li>Outlets exclusively devoted to empirical software engineering research\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://link.springer.com/journal/10664\">Empirical Software Engineering journal</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.msrconf.org/\">MSR: Mining Software Repositories conference</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://promise.site.uottawa.ca/SERepository/\">PROMISE: Predictive Models and Data Analytics in Software Engineering conference</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>","updatedAt":"2019-02-27T08:36:19.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Research Outlets</h2>","itemHTML":"<li>Outlets that publish empirical software engineering research\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://dl.acm.org/citation.cfm?id=J790\">ACM Transactions on Software Engineering and Methodology (TOSEM)</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.esec-fse.org/\">ESEC/FSE: ACM Joint European Software Engineering Conference and Symposium on the Foundations of Software Engineering</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.icse-conferences.org/\">ICSE: International Conference on Software Engineering</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://publications.computer.org/software-magazine/\">IEEE Software magazine</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.computer.org/csdl/journal/ts\">IEEE Transactions on Software Engineering</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.journals.elsevier.com/journal-of-systems-and-software\">Journal of Systems and Software</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://ieeexplore.ieee.org/xpl/conhome.jsp?punumber=1000695\">SANER: IEEE International Conference on Software Analysis, Evolution and Reengineering</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>","updatedAt":"2019-02-27T08:36:19.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Repositories</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://zenodo.org/\">Zenodo</a> - Software data collections in CERN's open-access repository.\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"http://zenodo.org/communities/seacraft\">Software Engineering Artifacts Can Really Assist Future Tasks</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://zenodo.org/communities/empirical-software-engineering/\">Empirical Software Engineering</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://zenodo.org/communities/msr/\">Mining Software Repositories</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>","updatedAt":"2019-02-27T07:47:44.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Repositories</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://sir.unl.edu/portal/index.php\">SIR</a> - Software-artifact infrastructure repository; Java, C, C++, and C# software together with test suites and fault data.</li>","updatedAt":"2019-02-27T07:25:36.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Repositories</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://promise.site.uottawa.ca/SERepository/datasets-page.html\">PROMISE</a> - About 20 datasets related to software engineering research.</li>","updatedAt":"2019-02-27T07:25:36.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Repositories</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://flossmole.org/collection_details\">FLOSSmole</a> - Collaborative collection and analysis of free/libre/open source project data.</li>","updatedAt":"2019-02-27T07:25:36.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Data Sets</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://androidtimemachine.github.io\">AndroidTimeMachine</a> - Graph-based dataset of commit history of 8,431 real-world Android apps.</li>","updatedAt":"2019-02-27T07:25:36.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Data Sets</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://androzoo.uni.lu/\">AndroZoo</a> - Collection of Android Applications.</li>","updatedAt":"2019-02-27T07:25:36.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Data Sets</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://bug.inf.usi.ch/index.php\">Bug Prediction Dataset</a> - Collection of models and metrics from Eclipse JDT Core, PDE UI, Equinox Framework, Lucene, Mylyn, and their histories.</li>","updatedAt":"2019-02-27T07:25:36.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Data Sets</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://kin-y.github.io/miningReviewRepo/\">Code Reviews</a> - Code reviews of OpenStack, LibreOffice, AOSP, Qt, Eclipse.</li>","updatedAt":"2019-02-27T07:25:36.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Data Sets</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://www.comp.nus.edu.sg/%7Erelease/corebench/\">CoREBench</a> - Collection of 70 realistically Complex Regression Errors that were systematically extracted from the repositories and bug reports of four open-source software projects: Make, Grep, Findutils, and Coreutils.</li>","updatedAt":"2019-02-27T07:25:36.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Data Sets</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://github.com/rjust/defects4j\">Defects4J</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/rjust/defects4j\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">462</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_I