accessible through Google's BigQuery platform.</li>","updatedAt":"2019-02-27T07:25:36.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Data Sets</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://www.kave.cc/datasets\">KaVE</a> - Developer tool interaction data.</li>","updatedAt":"2019-02-27T07:25:36.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Data Sets</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://github.com/bkarak/data_msr2015\">Maven metrics</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/bkarak/data_msr2015\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">0</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCount\":0,\"repo\":\"bkarak/data_msr2015\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END--> - Collection of software complexity &#x26; sizing metrics for the <a href=\"https://maven.apache.org\">Maven Repository</a>.</li>","updatedAt":"2019-02-27T07:25:36.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Data Sets</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://zenodo.org/record/1489120\">Maven Dependency Graph</a> - Snapshot of the whole Maven Central taken on September 6, 2018, stored in a graph database.</li>","updatedAt":"2019-02-27T07:25:36.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Data Sets</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://github.com/jxshin/mzdata\">mzdata</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/jxshin/mzdata\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;b