ans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">4</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCount\":4,\"repo\":\"tue-mdse/ocl-dataset\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END--> - Data set of 9188 OCL expressions originating from 504 EMF meta-models in 245 systematically selected GitHub repositories.</li>","updatedAt":"2019-02-27T07:25:36.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Data Sets</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://reporeapers.github.io\">RepoReapers Data Set</a> - Data set containing a collection of <em>engineered software projects</em> from GHTorrent.</li>","updatedAt":"2019-02-27T07:25:36.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Data Sets</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://stamina.chefbe.net/download\">STAMINA</a> - (STAte Machine INference Approaches) data are used to benchmark techniques for learning deterministic finite state machines (FSMs).</li>","updatedAt":"2019-02-27T07:25:36.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Data Sets</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://archive.org/details/stackexchange\">Stack Exchange</a> - Anonymized dump of all user-contributed content on the Stack Exchange network.</li>","updatedAt":"2019-02-27T07:25:36.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Data Sets</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://travistorrent.testroots.org\">TravisTorrent</a> - Provides free and easy-to-use Traivs CI build analyses.</li>","updatedAt":"2019-02-27T07:25:36.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Data Sets</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://wiki.debian.org/UltimateDebianDatabase\">Ultimate Debian Database (UDD)</a> - Data about various aspects of Debian (e.g. packages, bugs, mainteners) in the same SQL database.</li>","updatedAt":"2019-02-27T07:25:36.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Data Sets</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://github.